just doesn=E2=80=99t make sense that a big proportion of the crew isn=E2=
=80=99t able to pull its=20
weight because they are undereducated, unproductive and constantly in need=
 of=20
handouts from the rest of us. The Navy wouldn=E2=80=99t tolerate it; neith=
