<P style=3D"MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=3DMsoNormal><FONT size=3D3><FONT =
  face=3D"Times New Roman"><SPAN style=3D"mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;=
 </SPAN>Every=20
kid in <st1:country-region w:st=3D"on"><st1:place   w:st=3D"on">Haiti</st1=
:place></st1:country-region> who grows up to be a surgeon or=20
